  <a href="http://www.swim-log.co.uk/" target="newwindow">Swim Log</a> A Windows based program   for swimmers, parents, and coaches to track a swimmers race times and training   in yards and meters. </li>
  <li><a href="http://www.goeasyware.com/" target="newwindow">EasyWare</a> Offers an &quot;easy to use&quot;   meet manager and a team manager program. A downloadable trial version is   available. Windows </li>
  <li><strong>Online Programs</strong></li>
  <li><a href="http://www.swimtrainers.com/" target="newwindow">Swim-IQ</a> Swim-IQ is a   collaborative learning management system for swimming and water safety. </li>
