    <a href="http://activeendurance.com/" target="newwindow">ActiveEndurance</a> ActiveEndurance provides industry-leading   online team signup and club management solutions for swimming. </li>
  <li><a href="http://www.swimmingtraining4life.com/" target="newwindow">3S</a> The 3S program offers   professional education, certification, and analytical tools for swim coaches,   online training plans for swimmers, and more. </li>
